# 🤖 AI RAG Chatbot using Endee

## 🚀 Overview
This project is a Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) chatbot that allows users to upload PDF documents and ask questions based on the content.

The system retrieves relevant information using semantic search and provides concise answers.

## 🔥 Features
- 📄 PDF Upload and Processing
- 🔍 Semantic Search using Embeddings
- 🤖 Intelligent Answer Generation (RAG)
- 💬 Works even without PDF (default knowledge base)
- 🌐 Streamlit Web Application

## 🧠 How It Works
1. User uploads a PDF or asks a question
2. Text is converted into embeddings
3. Relevant chunks are retrieved using similarity search
4. System generates a meaningful answer from retrieved data

## 🏗️ Architecture
User Query → Embedding → Vector Search → Retrieved Context → Answer

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions
```bash
pip install -r rag_chatbot/requirements.txt
streamlit run rag_chatbot/app.py